HEADWORD: Afterclap
<hw>Aft"er*clap`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An unexpected
subsequent event; something disagreeable happening after an affair is
supposed to be at an end.</def> <rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
